name: hydroxyisourate hydrolase
classes: Acting on carbon-nitrogen bonds, other than peptide bonds;
comment: The reaction is the first stage in the conversion of 5-hydroxyisourate into S-allantoin. This reaction will also occur spontaneously but more slowly.
